Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: hostout.centos
Version: 0.1
Summary: Plugin for collective.hostout that bootstraps a CentOS host ready for hostout deployment
Home-page: https://svn.plone.org/svn/collective/hostout.centos
Author: Nejc Zupan
Author-email: nejc.zupan@niteoweb.com
